1948;;The Sign of the Ram;;American;;John Sturges;;Susan Peters, Alexander Knox;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Sign_of_the_Ram;;The story tells of Leah St. Aubyn (Peters) an invalid wife and mother who uses dictatorial control over everyone she knows. Leah's family forgive her temperament due to her medical condition, yet she exploits that fact fully. Eventually her behavior leaves her alone and without friends. Yet, even in her dark moments she insists upon "controlling all." Finally, she engineers her own death.